%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Captain%20Sully%20and%20the%20FAA%20are%20warning%20against%20plans%20to%20force%20pilots%20to%20retire%20later%20%E2%80%94%20as%20aviation%20safety%20comes%20into%20laser%20focus%20during%20the%20Boeing%20scandal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222940%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pilot%20Chesley%20'Sully'%20Sullenberger%20looks%20right%20at%20home%20in%20the%20cockpit%20aboard%20US%20Airways%20flight%201050%20to%20New%20York%2C%20it%20is%20his%20first%20flight%20since%20landing%20a%20commercial%20plane%20in%20the%20Hudson%20River.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c4c42c43bb77284ba4d6c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222310%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECaptain%20Chesley%20%26quot%3BSully%26quot%3B%20Sullenberger.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Theodorakis%2FNY%20Daily%20News%20Archive%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECongress%20is%20working%20on%20a%20bill%20to%20reauthorize%20the%20FAA%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20measure%20could%20include%20raising%20the%20age%20pilots%20need%20to%20retire%20from%2065%20to%2067.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20FAA%20warned%20it%20needs%20more%20data%20first%2C%20while%20Captain%20Sully%20strongly%20opposed%20the%20move.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Chesley%20'Sully'%20Sullenberg%20and%20aviation%20regulators%20are%20warning%20Congress%20against%20raising%20the%20mandatory%20retirement%20age%20for%20pilots%20to%2067.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECongress%20is%20working%20on%20a%20bill%20to%20extend%20the%20authorization%20of%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20for%20five%20years.%20Last%20year%2C%20it%20failed%20to%20pass%20a%20bill%20before%20the%20deadline%2C%20which%20it%20then%20temporarily%20extended%20to%20March%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20July%2C%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives%20passed%20a%20bill%20that%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2