E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2Fsecurity-aviation%2F2024-02-04%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2Fisraeli-army-its-admits-staff-was-behind-graphic-gaza-telegram-channel%2F0000018d-70b4-dd6e-a98d-f4b6a9c00000%5C%22%3Ehas%20admitted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20its%20Influencing%20Department%20has%20been%20illegally%20running%20a%20Telegram%20channel%20that%20has%20been%20posting%20and%20sharing%20gory%20images%20of%20killings%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20as%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20war%20while%20also%20sharing%20inside%20information%20from%20IDF%20investigations%20to%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20%3Cem%3EHaaretz%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20one%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20largest%20circulated%20newspapers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2Fsecurity-aviation%2F2023-12-12%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2Fgraphic-videos-and-incitement-how-the-idf-is-misleading-israelis-on-telegram%2F0000018c-5ab5-df2f-adac-febd01c30000%5C%22%3Eexposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Telegram%20group%2C%20called%20%E2%80%9972%20Virgins%20%E2%80%93%20Uncensored%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20second%20week%20of%20December%20last%20year%2C%20IDF%20denied%20running%20any%20such%20online%20group.%20However%2C%20reversing%20its%20earlier%20statement%2C%20IDF%20admitted%20on%20Febrary%204%20that%20the%20group%20is%20operated%20by%20members%20of%20a%20department%20of%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%E2%80%99%20Operations%20Directorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20on%20October%209%2C%20the%20Telegram%20group%20has%20been%20sharing%20hundreds%20of%20grotesque%20still%20images%20and%20videos%20of%20dying%20Palestinians%20with%20captions%20accompanying%20them%20that%20describe%20Palestinians%20as%20%E2%80%9Croaches%E2%80%9D%2C%20calling%20for%20their%20%E2%80%9Cextermination%E2%80%9D.%20The%20intention%20of%20the%20racist%20channel%20appears%20to%20be%20