ose%20very%20legacies%20and%20strengths%20%E2%80%94%20as%20the%20means%20of%20the%20marginalised%20are%20limited%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20might%20of%20the%20oppressive%20forces.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20speech%20was%20made%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20assembly%2C%20it%20resonated%20across%20tribal%20groups%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpre-election-swoop-central-agencies-latest-trick-opposition-leaders%5C%22%3Eweaponisation%20of%20central%20agencies%20by%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%3C%2Fa%3E%20(BJP)%20against%20the%20opposition%20is%20an%20open%20secret.%20However%2C%20two%20arguments%2C%20seem%20obvious%20here.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20%E2%80%98has%E2%80%99%20committed%20a%20crime%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20it%20necessitates%20the%20role%20of%20the%20central%20investigation%20agencies%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20this%20case%2C%20to%20step%20in%2C%20investigate%2C%20and%20hold%20him%20accountable.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecond%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20as%20a%20party%20leader%20of%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%20and%20who%20is%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20he%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20vendetta%20politics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20corruption.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAny%20corrupt%20practice%20is%20problematic%2C%20and%20regardless%20of%20who%20commits%20it%2C%20it%20should%20be%20subject%20to%20scrutiny%2C%20investigation%2C%20and%20necessary%20action%20by%20the%20relevant%20authorities.%20The%20issue%20here%20is%20about%20intentionality%20and%20lack%20of%20transparency%20as%20to%20why%20and%20how%20certain%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20are%20probed%20with%20alacrity%2C%20while%20others%20are%20ignored%2C%20postponed%2C%20or%20buried%20by%20the%20central%20agencies%20(e.g.%20the%20Sahara%20Diaries%2C%20the%20Ahmedabad%20Cooperative%20Bank%20scam%20in%20Gujarat%20during%20demonetisation).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAre%20the%20institutions%20of%20the%20state%20(e.g.%20the%20ED%2FCBI%2FIncome%20Tax%20department)%20doing%20what%20they%20are%20mandated%20to%2C%20and%20in%20the%20manner%20they%20are%20supposed%20to%3F%20The%20jury%20is%20(still)%20out.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20of%20the%20time%2C%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20public%20memory%20is%20obfuscated%20with%20charges%20of%20defamation%20and%20counter-defamation%20by%20the%20concerned%20alleging%2C%20accused%2C%20and%20repudiating%20parties%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fnews-ians%2Fbank-with-amit-shah-as-a-director-collected-highest-amount-of-banned-notes-among-dccbs-rti-reply-118062100425_1.html%5C%22%3Ewith%20no%20real%20outcome%20%E2%80%93%20until%20it%20fades%20public%20memory%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20point%20is%2C%20the%20corruption%20of%20the%20Savarnas%20in%20the%20loot%20of%20public%20money%20and%20public%20assets%20is%20not%20only%20normalised%20but%20armed%20with%20impunity%3B%20but%20those%2C%20if%20committed%20or%20alleged%20to%20have%20been%20committed%20by%20the%20Bahujans%20(Adivasis%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20the%20OBCs)%2C%20then%20the%20Savarna%20state%20apparatus%20(the%20legislative%2C%20executive%2C%20judiciary%2C%20and%20the%20corporate%20media)%20swings%20into%20action%3A%20ensuring%20that%20the%20issue%20made%20a%20spectacle%20of%20in%20the%20public%20eye.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20purpose%20is%20to%20remind%20us%20of%20existing%20unchecked%20hegemonies%2C%20reinforce%20who%E2%80%99s%20in%20power%2C%20and%20the%20manifold%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20Bahujan%20including%20the%20religious%20minorities%20can%20be%20shown%20their%20place%2C%20even%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%20and%20due%20process.%20Morality%20and%20ethics%20evade%20similar%20scrutiny%20and%20treatment%20in%20cases%20that%20pertain%20to%20the%20non-Bahujans.%20Overall%2C%20those%20pliant%20to%20the%20BJP%20are%20spared%20the%20scrutiny%20and%20action%2C%20and%20the%20defiant%20demonised%20in%20no%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecond%20is%20the%20issue%20of%20politics.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20stealth%2C%20slyness%2C%20and%20brazenness%20with%20which%20BJP%20attempts%20to%20destabilise%20elected%20governments%20in%20contemporary%20politics%20are%20plain%20to%20see.%20The%20country%20has%20seen%20this%20play%20out%20on%20a%20repeat%20mode%20for%20a%20good%20number%20of%20years%20now%20in%20different%20states%20%E2%80%94%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Bihar%2C%20and%20now%20Jharkhand.%20It%20follows%20the%20same%20familiar%20script.%20The%20BJP%20sets%20the%20agenda%2C%20the%20central%20agencies%20spring%20into%20prompt%20action%2C%20and%20the%20corporate%20media%20prostrates%20on%20cue%2C%20peddling%20a%20curated%20narrative%20that%20works%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20government.%20This%20time%20too%2C%20the%20mainstream%20media%2C%20before%20due%20process%2C%20played%20the%20predictable%20role%20of%20magnifying%20Hemant%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20crime.%20Some%20TV%20anchors%20demonising%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20and%20what%20he%20is%20worth%20and%20deserving%20of%2C%20exposed%20their%20casteist%20mindsets.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20CM%2C%20Champai%20Soren%20may%20have%20won%20the%20floor%20test%3B%20but%20the%20danger%20of%20destabilisation%20for%20the%20state%20government%20still%20lurks.%20Champai%20Soren%2C%20and%20the%20completion%20of%20JMM%20and%20its%20allied%20parties%E2%80%99s%20full%20term%20is%20not%20the%20issue%20at%20hand%2C%20but%20the%20potential%20return%20of%20Hemant%20Soren%20in%20Jharkhand%20politics%20is%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20RSS.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20Hemant%20Soren%20is%20the%20proverbial%20enemy%20within%20the%20fascist%20Hindutva%20imagination.%20Five%20key%20aspects%20of%20his%20politics%20and%20decision-making%20in%20the%20past%20four%20years%20illustrate%20my%20point.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FWCp__8kETUY%3Fsi%3Dfzp0nCkTdP5aKjXb%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%2C%20announcing%20the%20intent%20to%20withdraw%20the%20cases%20of%20the%20Pathalgadi%20movement%20in%202019%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Raghubir%20Das%20government%20of%20the%20BJP%20framed%20sedition%20charges%20against%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20Adivasis%20and%20their%20leaders%20of%20the%20Pathalgadi%20movement%20between%202017%20and%202018.%20Soon%20after%20taking%20charge%20of%20the%20government%2C%20the%20Hemant%20Soren-led%20government%20in%20its%20first%20cabinet%20meeting%20on%20December%2029%2C%202019%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F944116%2F10000-people-charged-with-sedition-in-one-jharkhand-district-what-does-democracy-mean-here%5C%22%3Eannounced%20the%20dropping%20of%20all%20the%20charges%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20right%20of%20the%20Adivasi%20to%20resist%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20assert%2C%20and%20claim%20their%20traditional%20customs%20and%20practices%2C%20in%20a%20way%20that%20is%20meaningful%20and%20empowering%20to%20them%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F4-years-after-announcement-soren-govt-yet-to-withdraw-cases-pending-against-pathalgadi-movement%5C%22%3EThough%20he%20has%20yet%20to%20fulfil%20that%20promise%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20announcing%20his%20intent%20to%20do%20that%20itself%20was%20a%20subversive%20move%20in%20such%20a%20skewed%20and%20polarised%20political%20climate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecond%2C%20puncturing%20the%20Hindutva%20narrative%20about%20Adivasis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20growing%20RSS%20and%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%E2%80%99s%20penetration%20into%20the%20Adivasi%20hinterlands%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20powerful%20stand%20that%20%E2%80%9CAdivasis%20were%20never%20Hindus%20and%20they%20never%20will%20be%E2%80%9D%20(2021)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fadivasis-were-never-hindus-they-never-will-be-jharkhand-cm-7199096%2F%5C%22%3Ecan%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20major%20impediment%20to%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20civilizing%20mission%20of%20the%20Adivasis%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20statement%20in%20a%20way%20has%20challenged%20the%20dominant%20narrative%20of%20Hindutva%20thinkers%20and%20their%20decades%20long%20politics%20that%20Adivasis%20are%20%E2%80%98%20backward%20Hindus%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20reiterated%20their%20claim%20that%20the%20Adivasis%20and%20tribals%20are%20the%20first%20peoples%20(indigenous)%20of%20this%20land%20%E2%80%94%20before%20the%20birth%2C%20and%20spread%20of%20any%20major%20religion(s)%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThird%2C%20advocacy%20for%20the%20Sarna%20Code%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20September%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fjharkhand-cm-soren-writes-to-pm-modi-seeks-recognition-of-sarna-religious-code-for-tribals%2Farticleshow%2F103983311.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EHemant%20Soren%20wrote%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20for%20the%20inclusion%20of%20%E2%80%98Sarna%20code%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20religion%20section%20of%20all%20future%20censuses%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20the%20movement%20for%20the%20inclusion%20of%20Tribal%2FSarna%20religious%20code%20in%20the%20census%20has%20had%20a%20long%20history%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20support%20and%20advocacy%20on%20this%20issue%20speaks%20to%20the%20concerns%20of%20millions%20of%20Adivasis%20and%20tribals%20across%20India.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ramifications%20of%20this%20can%20be%20significant%2C%20especially%20for%20Hindutva%20politics%20which%20is%20based%20on%20the%20idea%20that%2080%25%20of%20the%20Indian%20population%20are%20Hindus.%20The%20fulfilment%20of%20their%20idea%20of%20India%20or%20Bharat%2C%20presumably%2C%20will%20come%20from%20this%20chunk%20of%20the%20population.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20victory%20of%20the%20Sarna%20Code%20Bill%20for%20tribal%20politics%2C%20whenever%20that%20is%2C%20will%20be%20important%2C%20especially%20for%20states%20like%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Jharkhand%20where%20attempts%20to%20create%20the%20%E2%80%98Other%E2%80%99%20within%20the%20tribal%20community%20between%20the%20converted%20and%20the%20non-converted%20is%20in%20full%20swing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETribals%20are%20either%20considered%20%E2%80%98backward%20Hindus%E2%80%99%2C%20who%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Eif%20they%20adopt%20foreign%20religions%20like%20Christianity%20and%20Islam%20ought%20to%20forego%20their%20rights%20completely.%20This%20idea%20disregards%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20issues%20and%20struggles%20of%20converted%20and%20non-converted%20tribals%20are%20the%20same%20i.e.%20dispossession%2C%20displacement%20and%20marginalisation%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20neoliberal%20capitalism%2C%20state-corporate%20nexus%2C%20and%20the%20Savarna%20state%20apparatus.%20There%20is%20little%20in%20common%20between%20an%20Adivasi%20Hindu%20and%20a%20Brahmin%20Hindu%2C%20given%20their%20different%20histories%2C%20stories%2C%20memories%2C%20and%20struggles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFourth%2C%20passing%20of%20the%201932%20Khatiyan%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20December%202023%2C%20the%20Hemant%20Soren%20government%2C%20despite%20contestations%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1037793%2Fwhy-does-jharkhand-want-to-go-back-to-1932-to-determine-who-is-a-jharkhandi%5C%22%3Epassed%20the%20new%20domicile%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%20titled%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Jharkhand%20Definition%20of%20Local%20Persons%20and%20for%20Extending%20the%20Consequential%20Social%2C%20Cultural%20and%20Other%20Benefits%20to%20such%20Local%20Persons%20Bill%2C%202022%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fjharkhand-assembly-once-again-passes-1932-khatiyan-bill%2Farticle67658409.ece%5C%22%3Ewith%20the%20sole%20idea%20of%20creating%20safeguards%20for%20the%20Adivasis%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20marginal%20groups%20of%20Jharkhand%20from%20the%20non-Adivasi%20early%20migrants%20to%20the%20area%2C%20on%20issues%20of%20employment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFifth%2C%20instituting%20the%20Marang%20Gomke%20Overseas%20Scholarships%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202021%2C%20one%20significant%20decision%20the%20Hemant%20Soren%20government%20took%20post-pandemic%20was%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20education%20sector.%20Through%20this%20scholarship%20instituted%20in%20the%20memory%20of%20Jaipal%20Singh%20Munda%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianhistorycollective.com%2Fjaipal-singh-munda-historyofindia-constituent-assembly-adivasirights%2F%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20tall%20Adivasi%20leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20full%20financial%20support%20is%20given%20to%2025%20students%20belonging%20to%20the%20SC%2FST%2FOBC%20and%20minority%20communities%20to%20pursue%20a%20Masters%20and%20MPhil%20from%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%20More%20scholarships%20for%20MPhil%20and%20PhD%20study%20abroad%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fwire-updates%2Fnational%2F2023%2F08%2F11%2Fces9-jh-scholarships-soren.html%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20live%20in%20interesting%20times.%20Some%20of%20our%20very%20own%2C%20have%20reached%20powerful%20positions%20in%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20as%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20and%20Hemant%20Soren%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20a%20state%2C%20both%20from%20the%20Santhal%20tribe%20%E2%80%93%20a%20rarity%20in%20Indian%20politics.%20The%20purpose%20of%20political%20representation%20in%20a%20representative%20democracy%20like%20ours%20has%20been%20to%20create%20space%20for%20the%20underrepresented%20groups%20to%20have%20a%20voice%2C%20and%20to%20work%20in%20their%20interest.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20tragedy%20is%20that%20the%20enviable%20position%20of%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20having%20held%20many%20senior%20posts%20and%20offices%2C%20has%20come%20with%20a%20cost%20to%20her%20voice%20and%20agency.%20That%20privileged%20position%20and%20access%20to%20power%20have%20only%20been%20used%20to%20embellish%20the%20crowns%20of%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20but%20to%20never%20stand%20up%20for%20herself%20or%20her%20people.%20For%20instance%2C%20accepting%20omission%20from%20the%20inauguration%20event%20of%20the%20new%20parliament%20building%20or%20failing%20to%20speak%20a%20few%20words%20on%20the%20Manipur%20incident%20of%20the%20tribal%20woman%20being%20paraded%20naked.%20But%20to%20be%20fair%20to%20her%2C%20what%20she%20said%20of%20incarceration%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forwardpress.in%2F2022%2F12%2Fwhen-the-president-spoke-for-the-dalitbahujan-and-what-she-left-unsaid%2F%5C%22%3Eneed%20to%20build%20fewer%20and%20not%20more%20jails%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20front%20of%20the%20senior%20members%20of%