to%20be%20some%20trade-offs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%202021%20through%202022%2C%20about%2027%2C000%20people%20moved%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%20from%20the%20US%20states%2C%20according%20to%20data%20collected%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Ftopics%2Fpopulation%2Fmigration%2Fguidance%2Fstate-to-state-migration-flows.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Census%20Bureau%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20territory's%20tax%20incentive%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.investpr.org%2Fwhy-puerto-rico%2Ftax-benefits-policy%2F%3Fnis%3D6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAct%2060%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20a%20big%20draw%20for%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20mainlanders%20can%20move%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%20without%20becoming%20citizens%2C%20if%20they%20do%20get%20citizenship%2C%20they%20can%20apply%20for%20a%2015-year%20decree%20under%20Act%2060.%20If%20approved%2C%20the%20person%20or%20business%20only%20has%20to%20pay%20a%204%25%20fixed%20rate%20on%20income%20and%20can%20receive%20a%2075%25%20reduction%20in%20property%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20individuals%20do%20not%20have%20to%20pay%20any%20taxes%20on%20capital%20gains%20accrued%20after%20becoming%20citizens%20and%20businesses%20benefit%20from%20a%2050%25%20reduction%20in%20municipal%20license%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fpuerto-rico-state-senate-eliminate-puerto-rico-s-act-60-act-20-22%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebenefits%20do%20have%20opponents%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20can%20be%20a%20political%20hot-button%20topic%20locally.%20According%20to%20Santana%2C%20politicians%20must%20find%20ways%20to%20appease%20native%20Puerto%20Ricans%20who%20are%20upset%20because%20they%20do%20not%20get%20the%20same%20tax%20breaks%20while%20also%20acknowledging%20quietly%20that%20the%20incentives%20are%20working%20to%20boost%20the%20island's%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20economic%20impact%20is%20real%2C%20but%20come%20prepared%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woman%20shopping%20in%20san%20juan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c28cfa7a3d2714887845e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESan%20Juan's%20shopping%20and%20nightlife%20have%20been%20compared%20to%20Miami.%3Cp%3EJessica%20Peterson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20big%20consideration%20before%20relocating%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%20is%20ensuring%20the%20entire%20family%20is%20on%20board%20and%20will%20have%20what%20they%20need%2C%20Santana%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20family%2C%20if%20your%20spouse%2C%20they%20can't%20adapt%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20how%20much%20taxes%20you're%20saving%2C%20it%20is%20not%20going%20to%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Santana%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20for%20families%20with%20young%20children%20is%20finding%20the%20right%20school%2C%20Santana%20said.%20He%20added%20there%20are%20several%20well-rated%20bilingual%20schools%20on%20the%20island%2C%20but%20they%20are%20struggling%20to%20handle%20the%20bandwidth%20of%20the%20growing%20population%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20areas%20deemed%20most%20desirable%20for%20the%20mainlanders%20moving%20to%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20areas%20is%20Dorado%2C%20a%20city%20about%2020%20miles%20west%20of%20San%20Juan%20on%20the%20island's%20north%20side%2C%20where%20many%20of%20the%20more%20expensive%20homes%20are%20being%20built.%20While%20a%20family%20may%20find%20the%20home%20and%20community%20they%20desire%20in%20that%20area%2C%20if%20there%20is%20no%20availability%20in%20the%20local%20school%2C%20the%20children%20may%20be%20forced%20to%20commute%2035%20to%2040%20minutes%20each%20way%20to%20a%20school%20in%20San%20Juan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Map%20of%20Puerto%20Rico%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c289766fcb546d2d4cba29%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222195%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMap%20of%20Puerto%20Rico.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EOther%20challenges%20include%20healthcare%20and%20services%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20big%20issue%20that%20people%20need%20to%20consider%20before%20moving%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%20is%20the%20state%20of%20the%20healthcare%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESarah%20Lindsey%20and%20Sean%20Flynn%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretire-puerto-rico-tax-benefits-healthcare-residency-requirements-real-estate-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20semi-retired%20couple%20that%20moved%20to%20Humacao%2C%20Puerto%20Rico%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20from%20Austin%20in%202021%2C%20previously%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etold%20Business%20Insider%20that%20healthcare%20insurance%20is%20cheap%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Byou're%20kind%20of%20getting%20what%20you%20paid%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESantana%20noted%20healthcare%20can%20be%20especially%20problematic%20if%20you%20need%20a%20specialist%20on%20the%20island.%20If%20you%20can%20find%20one%2C%20there%20might%20be%20a%20long%20wait%2C%20and%20other%20times%2C%20you%20might%20need%20to%20fly%20to%20Miami%20or%20New%20York%20for%20the%20necessary%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPuerto%20Rico%20was%20already%20in%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F26551268%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehealthcare%20crisis%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%202015%2C%20and%20the%20situation%20worsened%20over%20the%20next%20three%20years.%20In%20the%20year%20following%20Hurricane%20Maria%20in%202017%2C%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fidentities%2F2020%2F2%2F27%2F21150176%2Fpuerto-rico-health-care-hospital-access-hurricane-maria%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E15%25%20of%20Puerto%20Rico's%20healthcare%20professionals%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20left%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELindsey%20noted%20that%20if%20somebody%20expressed%20interest%20in%20moving%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20she%20would%20first%20ask%20them%20about%20their%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20you%20want%20to%20go%20down%20there%2C%20but%20if%20you%20have%20some%20health%20problems%2C%20maybe%20you%20don't%2C%26quot%3B%20Lindsey%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20really%20better%20for%20people%20who%20are%20younger%20and%20healthier.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20and%20US%20governments%20are%20working%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2023%2F06%2F26%2Ffact-sheet-biden-harris-administration-steadfast-in-support-of-puerto-ricos-renewal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eimprove%20healthcare%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Lindsey%20and%20Flynn%20noted%20there%20is%20a%20specific%20effort%20being%20made%20to%20add%20clinics%20that%20might%20cater%20better%20to%20older%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Puerto%20Rico%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c28dea7a3d2714887846ce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20are%20young%20and%20adventurous%2C%20Puerto%20Rico%20could%20be%20a%20perfect%20fit.%3Cp%3EKimberly%20Sue%20Walker%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESantana%20also%20warns%20clients%20about%20the%20need%20for%20patience%20on%20the%20island%2C%20especially%20with%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20must%20understand%20that%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20little%20laid%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20lure%20of%20tax%20breaks%20has%20real%20estate%20prices%20rising%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Puerto%20Rico%20is%20a%20US%20territory%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthepuertoricorealestate.com%2Fyour-questions-about-puerto-rico%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20mainlanders%20can%20buy%20real%20estate%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20island%20without%20any%20restrictions.%20The%20influx%20of%20American%20mainlanders%20has%20affected%20the%20island's%20high-end%20real%20estate%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20years%20ago%2C%20developers%20were%20focused%20on%20building%20houses%20that%20ranged%20between%20%242%20million%20and%20%244%20million%2C%20Santana%20said.%20Now%2C%20developers%20are%20creating%20homes%20that%20cost%20between%20%2420%20million%20and%20%2440%20million%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20mind-boggling%20that%20the%20kind%20of%20individuals%20moving%20to%20the%20island%2C%20we%20didn't%20necessarily%20have%20that%20particular%20inventory%20available%2C%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehe%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20developers%20have%20changed%20to%20adapt%20to%20the%20new%20demands.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221123%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20house%20for%20sale%20in%20Dorado%2C%20Puerto%20Rico.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c28ebd7a3d27148878473d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22866%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20%2420%20million%20house%20for%20sale%20in%20Dorado%2C%20Puerto%20Rico.%3Cp%3ECollectivo%20Group%20Real%20Estate%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPrices%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eare%20more%20reasonable%20in%20some%20areas%2C%20such%20as%20Flynn%20and%20Lindsey's%20new%20home%20of%20Humacao%2C%20which%20is%20about%2090%20minutes%20from%20San%20Juan%20on%20the%20island's%20southeast%20coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20where%20transplants%20settle%2C%20they%20may%20encounter%20difficulties%20finding%20necessities%20like%20chairs%2C%20beds%2C%20and%20couches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sale%20of%20