%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMembers%20of%20the%20Climbing%20Kilimanjaro%20team%20summiting%20Kilimanjaro.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Stephen%20Mtui%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJustin%20Stephen%20Mtui%20has%20climbed%20Mount%20Kilimanjaro%20over%20300%20times%20as%20a%20porter%20and%20guide.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20started%20his%20tour%20company%20Climbing%20Kilimanjaro%20in%202008%20to%20improve%20the%20treatment%20of%20porters.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMtui%20said%20even%20fit%2C%20healthy%20tourists%20are%20often%20unprepared%20for%20how%20difficult%20the%20hike%20can%20be.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20story%20is%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%20Justin%20Stephen%20Mtui%2C%20a%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.climbing-kilimanjaro.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EKilimanjaro%20summit%20guide%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20clarity%20and%20length.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20been%20an%20active%20hiker%20and%20hiked%20local%20hills%20and%20mountains%20in%20Tanzania.%20Climbing%20Mount%20Kilimanjaro%20was%20a%20personal%20goal%2C%20but%20the%20only%20way%20I%20could%20do%20it%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20was%20as%20a%20porter.%20Government%20regulations%20on%20hiking%20meant%20you%20had%20to%20be%20taken%20to%20the%20summit%20by%20a%20guide%20or%20work%20for%20a%20tour%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20weren't%20a%20lot%20of%20high-paying%20jobs%20in%20Tanzania%2C%20so%20becoming%20a%20porter%20for%20a%20tour%20company%20was%20a%20good%20financial%20decision%20that%20also%20came%20with%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hike%20is%20seven%20days%20%E2%80%94%20about%20three%20and%20a%20half%20days%20up%20the%20mountain%20and%20three%20and%20a%20half%20days%20back.%20It's%20filled%20with%20amazing%20flora%2C%20fauna%2C%20and%20its%20fair%20share%20of%20challenges.%20Hikers%20can%20experience%20altitude%20sickness%2C%20and%20we%20can%20encounter%20challenges%20with%20camps%20and%20health%20and%20safety%20like%20any%20extreme%20sport.%20I've%20climbed%20Kilimanjaro%20over%20300%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Justin%20Stephen%20Mtui%20is%20a%20guide%20and%20tour%20operator%20for%20Climbing%20Kilimanjaro.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c37d4943bb77284ba455da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJustin%20Stephen%20Mtui%20has%20climbed%20Mount%20Kilimanjaro%20over%20300%20times.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Stephen%20Mtui%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20hike%20is%20grueling%20for%20porters%20with%20heavy%20luggage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20porter%20carries%20a%20climber's%20luggage%20on%20their%20back%20while%20the%20guide%20leads%20groups%20of%20hikers%20toward%20the%20summit.%20It%20was%20grueling.%20Sometimes%2C%20I'd%20have%2035%20kilograms%20on%20my%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20hike%20up%20Mount%20Kilimanjaro%20was%20my%20first%20time%20hiking%20with%20big%20luggage.%20I%20thought%20about%20quitting%20many%20times%20during%20that%20first%20hike.%20Halfway%20up%20the%20mountain%2C%20the%20other%20porter%20decided%20he%20couldn't%20do%20it.%20I%20stuck%20it%20out%20because%20porters%20are%20well-paid%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20I'd%20struggle%20to%20find%20a%20better%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPorters%20don't%20usually%20get%20to%20the%20summit%2C%20but%20after%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20I%20grabbed%20all%20the%20gear%20I'd%20need%20and%20stayed%20with%20a%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20summit%20is%20the%20most%20amazing%20thing%20I've%20ever%20experienced.%20I%20remember%20telling%20other%20porters%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20haven't%20gone%20to%20Kilimanjaro%20summit%2C%20you%20can't%20say%20you're%20hiking%20Kilimanjaro.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20hikers%20reach%20the%20summit%20of%20Mount%20Kilimanjaro.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c37daa6fcb546d2d4ce7e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20group%20of%20hikers%20reach%20the%20summit%20of%20Mount%20Kilimanjaro.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Stephen%20Mtui%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20became%20a%20guide%20in%20a%20transitional%20period%20in%20the%20industry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%20in%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20porters%20had%20to%20bring%20their%20own%20food%20and%20gear.%20You%20had%20little%20control%20over%20your%20income%20or%20the%20tips.%20The%20guide%20controlled%20your%20pay%2C%20and%20getting%20a%20shot%20as%20a%20porter%20was%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20change%20how%20porters%20were%20paid%20and%20give%20hikers%20a%20better%20experience%2C%20so%20I%20became%20a%20guide.%20I%20had%20to%20take%20a%20course%20and%20a%20basic%20exam%20to%20ensure%20I%20could%20safely%20get%20people%20to%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20taking%20people%20up%20Mount%20Kilimanjaro%20with%20my%20company%2C%20Climbing%20Kilimanjaro%2C%20around%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEvery%20hike%20starts%20with%20information%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20you've%20researched%20before%20arriving%20at%20Kilimanjaro%2C%20there's%20much%20to%20learn.%20I%20lead%20the%20hikers%2C%20help%20them%20navigate%20the%20environment%2C%20and%20provide%20physical%20and%20emotional%20support.%20Every%20morning%20and%20evening%2C%20I%20prepare%20the%20group%20so%20they%20know%20what%20to%20expect%20on%20that%20day%20of%20the%20hike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20guide%2C%20I%20run%20my%20crew%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20chef%20and%20all%20the%20porters.%20I%20have%20to%20check%20that%20everyone%20has%20the%20right%20equipment%2C%20and%20at%20every%20camp%20stop%2C%20I%20assess%20the%20team's%20well-being%20and%20ensure%20that%20every%20area%20at%20each%20campsite%20is%20operational.%20I%20also%20ensure%20the%20porters%20are%20fed%2C%20the%20tents%20are%20well-pitched%2C%20and%20everyone%20is%20happy%20and%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hikers%20prepare%20for%20a%20day%20of%20hiking%20by%20stretching%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c37e027a3d271488787066%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHikers%20prepare%20for%20a%20day%20of%20hiking%20with%20stretching.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Stephen%20Mtui%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20industry%20has%20changed%20over%20the%20years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20internet%2C%20tourists%20would%20arrive%20with%20their%20Lonely%20Planet%20guide%2C%20and%20we'd%20know%20they%20were%20coming%20to%20climb%20or%20do%20a%20safari.%20They%20would%20bring%20a%20hiking%20bag%20and%20equipment%20or%20lots%20of%20money%20to%20book%20a%20local%20tour%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20industry%20has%20changed%20a%20lot%20since%20then.%20I%20started%20my%20company%20when%20people%20transitioned%20to%20looking%20up%20travel%20operators%20online.%20I've%20had%20to%20learn%20to%20be%20a%20digital%20marketer%20because%20people%20now%20reserve%20and%20pre-pay%20online%20and%20plan%20their%20trips%20much%20rather%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20has%20helped%20make%20the%20Kilimanjaro%20hike%20more%20popular.%20It's%20more%20common%20for%20travelers%20to%20see%20smiling%20photos%20from%20the%20summit%20of%20Kilimanjaro%20online%20and%20book%20without%20knowing%20what%20the%20climb%20requires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMany%20tourists%20arrive%20unprepared%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20we%20start%20a%20hike%2C%20we%20check%20that%20every%20climber%20has%20the%20necessary%20gear.%20Some%20people%20get%20altitude%20sickness%2C%20too%2C%20and%20I've%20had%20to%20do%20evacuations.%20We%20try%20to%20prepare%20people%20as%20best%20as%20possible%2C%20but%20it's%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20time%2C%20a%20lady%20showed%20up%20dressed%20like%20she%20was%20on%20a%20beach%20vacation.%20I%20warned%20her%20that%20it%20was%20a%20tough%20mountain.%20She%20didn't%20realize%20it%20would%20be%20multiple%20days%20of%20camping.%20After%20day%20two%2C%20she%20turned%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20don't%20realize%20there's%20no%20showering%20for%20seven%20days%20to%20get%20to%20the%20summit%20and%20back.%20For%20even%20limited%20cellphone%20reception%2C%20you%20must%20get%20a%20local%20SIM%20card%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20thing%20you%20can%20do%20on%20the%20mountain%20is%20hike%20and%20be%20in%20nature.%20It's%20a%20very%20secluded%20world.%20The%20most%20common%20thing%20people%20say%20when%20they%20reach%20the%20summit%20is%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20hardest%20thing%20I've%20ever%20done%20in%20my%20entire%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20hikers%20at%20the%20summit%20of%20Kilimanjaro.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c37e397a3d271488787071%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20group%20of%20hikers%20at%20the%20summit%20of%20Kilimanjaro.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Stephan%20Mtui%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGetting%20to%20the%20summit%20is%20the%20most%20rewarding%20experience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20guide%2C%20I%20have%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20anything.%20Other%20than%20altitude%20sickness%2C%20which%20is%20the%20biggest%20risk%2C%20we've%20had%20many%20times%20where%20someone's%20so%20tired%20that%20we%20have%20to%20help%20them%20go%20to%20the%20bathroom%20and%20physically%20pull%20their%20pants%20down.%20Even%20some%20physically%20fit%20people%20are%20completely%20exhausted%20by%20the%20end%20of%20a%20hike%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20people%20reach%20the%20top%2C%20they%20feel%20like%20they've%20conquered%20the%20world.%20Time%20stops%20for%20them.%20The%20oldest%20hiker%20I've%20helped%20summit%20was%20a%2075-year-old%20man.%20He%20found%20it%20difficult%20but%20was%20so%20happy%20when%20he%20reached%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20hiking%20with%20people%20from%20different%20countries%20and%20cultures.%20Everyone%20%E2%80%94%20myself%20included%20%E2%80%94%20learns%20a%20lot%20from%20their%20fellow%20hikers%20and%20the%20people%20they%20share%20a%20base%20camp%20with.%20I've%20learned%20not%20to%20underestimate%20anyone.%20People%20can%20push%20through%20a%20lot%20for%20the%20reward%20of%20getting%20to%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20company%2C%20we'll%20summit%20Kilimanjaro%2066%20times%20in%202024.%20It's%20exhausting%2C%20but%2C%20in%20the%20moment%2C%20you%20forget%20about%20it%20because%20you%20are%20excited%20to%20give%20people%20the%20best%20experience%20and%20help%20them%20fulfill%20their%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclimbing-mount-kilimanjaro-what-to-expect-guide-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707387073000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c37ce443bb77284ba455c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclimbing-mount-kilimanjaro-what-to-expect-guide-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Having%20summited%20Kilimanjaro%20over%20300%20times%2C%20this%20guide%20shares%20what%20to%20expect.%20He%20said%20to%20prepare%20to%20be%20so%20tired%20you'll%20need%20help%20going%20to%20the%20toilet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ashley%20Couto)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclimbing-mount-kilimanjaro-what-to-expect-guide-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chipotle%20says%20