urabh_Unmute%2Fstatus%2F1755500944748331350%5C%22%3Eare%20coming%20in%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20farmers%20having%20blocked%20the%20Noida-Greater%20Noida%20Expressway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08141221%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-08-at-1.00.10-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08141221%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-08-at-1.00.10-PM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08141221%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-08-at-1.00.10-PM-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08141221%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-08-at-1.00.10-PM-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696220%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFarmers%20at%20the%20Delhi-UP%20border.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2Fnoida-farmers-open-front-against-ntpc-dadri-agitation-continues%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThese%2520farmers%2520of%252024%2520villages%2Calso%2520launched%2520a%2520long%2520movement.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20On%20December%2018%2C%202023%2C%20farmers%20sat%20on%20strike%20in%20front%20of%20the%20NTPC%20office%20located%20in%20Noida%20Sector-24.%20After%20the%20police%20stopped%20the%20protesters%20some%20distance%20before%20the%20main%20gate%20of%20NTPC%2C%20they%20staged%20a%20day%20and%20night%20strike%20there.%20These%20farmers%20of%2024%20villages%20say%20that%20they%20are%20affected%20by%20NTPC%E2%80%99s%20Dadri%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20protest%20is%20being%20led%20by%20Bharatiya%20Kisan%