c%20structure%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20North%20Eastern%20States%20bordering%20Myanmar.%20Since%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20process%20of%20scrapping%20it%2C%20MHA%20has%20recommended%20the%20immediate%20suspension%20of%20the%20FMR.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20report%20on%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20says%20that%20a%20nine-member%20delegation%20of%20Kuki-Zo%20groups%20met%20a%20team%20of%20officials%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20on%20February%207.%20The%20government%20team%20was%20led%20by%20A.K%20Mishra%2C%20Adviser%2C%20Northeast%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20and%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20officials.%20Concerns%20over%20the%20scrapping%20of%20the%20Free%20Movement%20Regime%20with%20Myanmar%20were%20raised%20at%20the%20three-hour%20long%20meeting%20and%20the%20January%2024%20Kangla%20Fort%20incident%20in%20Imphal%20when%20Arambai%20Tenggol%2C%20a%20radical%20Meitei%20group%2C%20administered%20oath%20to%20elected%20representatives%20to%20supposedly%20%E2%80%98protect%20the%20integrity%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tribal%20delegation%20is%20also%20reported%20to%20have%20broached%20concerns%20over%20%E2%80%9Ccontinued%20power%20outages%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20of%20Churachandpur%20and%20Pherzawl%2C%E2%80%9D%20where%20hill%20tribals%20mostly%20reside.%20The%20territorial%20divisions%20across%20the%20sensitive%20border%20state%20have%20acquired%20political%20dimensions%20after%20the%20state%20has%20been%20in%20a%20state%20of%20turmoil%20since%20May%203%2C%20with%20over%20200%20persons%20dead%2C%20around%20300%20churches%20vandalised%20or%20destroyed%20and%2067%2C000%20persons%20internally%20displaced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20delegate%20who%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20meeting%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%20for%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20is%20still%20on%20the%20table%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20would%20continue%20to%20press%20for%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20meeting%20follows%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20Delhi%20visit%20on%20February%203%2C%20when%20he%20met%20Amit%20Shah.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20Shah%20announced%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20fence%20the%20entire%201%2C643-km%20border%20with%20Myanmar%2C%20with%20direct%20consequences%20for%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20who%20share%20ethnic%20ties%20with%20those%20across%20the%20border%20who%20earlier%20had%20permission%20to%20travel%20freely%20across%20the%20borders%20for%20upto%20a%20fortnight%20and%20stay%20within%2016%20kms%20of%20the%20other%E2%80%99s%20territory.%20Two%20chief%20ministers%20of%20the%20northeast%2C%20from%20Mizoram%20and%20Nagaland%20have%20also%20opposed%20the%20plans%20to%20fence%20off%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20on%20a%20long%20election%20campaign%20in%20Karnataka%20when%20trouble%20first%20broke%20out%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fby-visiting-assam-and-avoiding-manipur-modi-proves-again-that-he-only-cares-for-a-looming-election%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20avoided%20travel%20to%20the%20state%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20not%20even%20spoken%20about%20it%20bar%20a%20seconds-long%20intervention%20when%20a%20video%20of%20a%20mob%20attacking%20two%20women%20went%20viral.%20His%20decision%20to%20not%20make%20a%20visit%20has%20come%20under%20fire.%20He%20did%20not%20even%20go%20to%20neighbouring%20Mizoram%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20state%20assembly%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707377648000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2F