%80%99s%20minority%20cell%20there%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-wins-chandigarh-mayoral-polls-amid-rigging-allegations%5C%22%3Ewas%20caught%20with%20his%20hands%20in%20the%20electoral%20till%2C%20as%20it%20were.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThinking%20that%20the%20CCTV%20cameras%20had%20been%20turned%20off%2C%20one%20of%20these%20inanimate%20but%20fair-minded%20watch%20dogs%20filmed%20this%20gentleman%E2%80%99s%20questionable%20conduct.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20video%20released%20by%20the%20channel%2C%20Masih%20can%20be%20seen%20picking%20and%20choosing%20ballot%20papers%2C%20marking%20eight%20and%20then%20dropping%20these%20in%20a%20tray.%20As%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20eight%20invalid%20votes%20%E2%80%93%20all%20cast%20for%20the%20AAP%2FCongress%20candidates%20%E2%80%93%20were%20knocked%20out%2C%20leading%20the%20BJP%20to%20win.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInevitably%2C%20the%20matter%20went%20to%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAstounded%20by%20videographed%20shenanigans%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwont-allow-democracy-to-be-murdered-cji-chandrachud-on-chandigarh-stolen-mayoral-election%5C%22%3EChief%20Justice%20called%20this%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmockery%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmurder%E2%80%9D%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdemocracy%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20stating%20further%20that%20the%20presiding%20officer%20ought%20to%20be%20prosecuted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20may%20recall%20how%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20a%20long%20chat%20with%20an%20election%20officer%20in%20Georgia%20during%20the%20US%20Presidential%20election%20of%202020%2C%20nudging%20him%20gently%20and%20otherwise%20to%20produce%20just%20an%20additional%2011%2C000%20or%20so%20votes%20to%20ensure%20his%20victory%20in%20Georgia.%20Alas%2C%20that%20man%20with%20a%20law-abiding%2C%20democratic%20conscience%20did%20not%20oblige.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FAW_Bdf_jGaA%3Fsi%3DvkPpRhuVzK5v4TMI%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20do%20not%20know%20as%20of%20now%20if%20Anil%20Masih%20in%20Chandigarh%20was%20acting%20on%20his%20own%20loyal%20volition%20or%20whether%20a%20call%20had%20gone%20out%20to%20him%20from%20the%20top%2C%20as%20it%20had%20in%20Georgia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecall%20the%20time%20when%20a%20former%20prime%20minister%20from%20the%20very%20same%20ruling%20party%20as%20now%20lost%20a%20government%20at%20the%20centre%20in%20New%20Delhi%20by%20one%2C%20repeat%20one%2C%20vote%20rather%20than%20resorting%20to%20any%20subterfuge%20to%20prevent%20such%20a%20dethronement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20was%20then.%20Now%20even%20a%20measly%20mayoral%20contest%20with%20all%20of%2036%20votes%20in%20the%20reckoning%20must%20be%20won%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20it%20takes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20citizens%20who%20still%20stand%20by%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20and%20fair%20elections%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20basic%20bedrock%20of%20democracy%20must%20wish%20to%20hear%20from%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20Chandigarh%20happening%2C%20especially%20in%20view%20of%20what%20the%20top%20court%20has%20had%20to%20say.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWide%20sections%20also%20speculate%20whether%20the%20Chandigarh%20%E2%80%98murder%20of%20democracy%E2%80%99%20may%20not%20after%20all%20be%20a%20preview%20of%20%E2%80%98slaughter%E2%80%99%20on%20a%20larger%20scale.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDo%20let%20us%20remember%20that%20a%20defining%20General%20Election%20for%20parliament%20is%20due%20in%20less%20than%20three%20months%2C%20and%20Modi%20has%20already%2C%20more%20than%20once%2C%20announced%20the%20things%20slated%20to%20happen%20in%20his%20%E2%80%9Cthird%20term%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eapriori%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eself-assurance%20seems%20both%20democratically%20unlovely%20and%20rather%20ominous%2C%20given%20the%20shameless%20transgression%20in%20Chandigarh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20all%2C%20some%20pollsters%2C%20among%20them%20those%20that%20tend%20to%20favour%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20have%20proffered%20the%20calculation%20that%20the%20exit%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%20from%20the%20IND%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ealliance%20is%20set%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Edamage%20the%20ruling%20combine%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Esubstantially%20in%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EBihar%20rather%20than%20add%20to%20its%20fortun%3C%2Fspan%3Ees%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20once%2C%20the%20disgust%20expressed%20by%20common%20Biharis%20is%20unreserved%20and%20bad%20news%20for%20those%20who%20brought%20about%20this%20latest%20unconscionably%20comical%20coup.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESame%20with%20the%20roughshod%20happenings%20in%20Jharkhand.%20There%20too%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20JMM%20seem%20well%20poised%20to%20win%20most%20of%20the%2014%20parliamentary%20seats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20resentment%20of%20the%20Adivasis%2C%20both%20Sarna%20and%20Christian%2C%20must%20be%20heard%20to%20be%20believed%2C%20as%20also%20the%20welcome%20they%20gave%20the%20Rahul%20Gandhi-led%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20raids%20by%20teams%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20morning%20of%20February%206%20on%20a%20slew%20of%20personnel%20associated%20with%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20in%20the%20Capital%20surfaced%20as%20the%20morning%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebaddi%20khabar%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20big%20news%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esome%20media%20channels%20also%20made%20bold%20to%20feature%20a%20simultaneous%20press%20conference%20by%20Atishi%20Singh%2C%20minister%20in%20the%20Kejriwal%20cabinet%2C.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20briefing%2C%20she%20accused%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20of%20violating%20Supreme%20Court%20guidelines%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20its%20investigations.%20The%20ED%20has%20strenuously%20denied%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20charges%20but%20the%20popular%20perception%20that%20what%20the%20agency%20is%20overseeing%20the%20%E2%80%98Enforcement%E2%80%99%20of%20is%20Dictatorship.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDemocracy%20already%20having%20been%20murdered%2C%20as%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20said%20in%20open%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImagine%20how%20fraught%20a%20mere%20D%20can%20be.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fbadri-raina%5C%22%3EBadri%20Raina%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0taught%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707375039000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08121514%2FUntitled-design-4-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmurder-of-democracy-supreme-court-chandigarh-narendra-modi-anil-massih%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Modi%20speaking%20of%20a%20third%20term%20seems%20both%20democratically%20unlovely%20and%20rather%20ominous%2C%20given%20th