opted%20a%20private%20member%20resolution%20on%20July%2026%2C%202022%2C%20urging%20the%20Centre%20to%20cancel%20all%20coal%20blocks%20in%20the%20Hasdeo%20Aranya%20region.%20They%20said%20a%20letter%20to%20this%20effect%20was%20also%20sent%20to%20the%20Centre%2C%20but%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20in%20the%20House%20began%20after%20Speaker%20Raman%20Singh%20declined%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20notice%20for%20an%20adjournment%20motion%2C%20demanding%20discussion%20on%20the%20issue.%20Legislative%20affairs%20minister%20Brijmohan%20Agrawal%20described%20the%20opposition%20demand%20as%20%E2%80%9Cunjustified%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20chair%20had%20already%20disallowed%20the%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20Congress%20government%2C%20headed%20by%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%2C%20resigned%20and%20even%20before%20BJP%20chief%20minister%20Vishnu%20Deo%20Sai%20took%20the%20oath%20of%20office%2C%20the%20principal%20chief%20conservator%20of%20forest%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20issued%20an%20order%20on%20December%2011%20last%20year%20to%20fell%2015%2C307%20trees%20on%2091.3%20hectares%20of%20forest%20land%20for%20a%20coal%20mine%20project%20in%20Hasdeo%20area%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Charandas%20Mahant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20how%20such%20an%20order%20could%20be%20issued%20by%20the%20forest%20department%20after%20the%20Assembly%20had%20already%20passed%20a%20private%20member%20resolution%20cancelling%20mines%20in%20the%20Hasdeo%20area.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20end%20of%20Hasdeo%20will%20also%20result%20in%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Bango%20Dam%20due%20to%20silting%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mahant%20said%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fchhattisgarh-assembly-erupts-over-hasdeo-aranya-tree-felling-issue-opposition-mlas-suspended%2Farticleshow%2F107492322.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E