A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-uniform-civil-code-live-in-relationships-registration-register-live-in-relationships-or-face-6-month-jail-uttarakhand-civil-code-5003753%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%20Revolutionised%20Digital%20Payments%20When%20Cash%20Was%20King%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prominent%20faces%20of%20India's%20fintech%20industry%2C%20is%20facing%20a%20big%20crisis%20in%20a%20race%20to%20save%20his%20revolutionary%20digital%20payments%20firm%20-%20Paytm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma%20faces%20the%20challenge%20to%20keep%20the%20company%20operations%20running%20and%20regain%20investors'%20confidence%20after%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20ordered%20Paytm's%20banking%20arm%20to%20stop%20most%20of%20its%20operations%20from%20March%201%20over%20the%20violation%20of%20norms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20marks%20a%20stunning%20twist%20in%20the%20Paytm%20story%2C%20which%20started%20from%20Aligarh%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma's%20hometown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20trained%20engineer%2C%20Mr%20Sharma%20set%20up%20internet%20connections%20at%20homes%20to%20make%20a%20living%20after%20completing%20his%20education.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20he%20came%20to%20be%20counted%20in%20the%20country's%20top-100%20richest%20club.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBig%20Push%20In%202016%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm%20was%20founded%20in%202010%20by%20Mr%20Sharma%20as%20a%20pre-paid%20mobile%20bill%20payment%20platform.%20The%20company%20expanded%20to%20facilitating%20online%20instant%20payments%20through%20the%20Unified%20Payments%20Interface%20(UPI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20push%20came%20with%20demonetisation%20in%202016%2C%20when%20Rs%20500%20and%20Rs%201%2C000%20currency%20notes%20were%20outlawed%20overnight%2C%20leaving%20millions%20struggling%20for%20cash.%20Many%20moved%20to%20online%20transactions%2C%20and%20Paytm%20emerged%20as%20a%20key%20player%2C%20quickly%20becoming%20the%20country's%20premier%20digital%20payments%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIPO%20Backlash%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm's%202021%20IPO%20valuation%20faced%20a%20backlash%20from%20investors%20and%20analysts%20when%20the%20stock%20plummeted%20on%20its%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20IPO%20opened%20on%20November%208%2C%202021%2C%20in%20the%20price%20band%20of%20Rs%202%2C080-2%2C150%20per%20share.%20The%20Paytm%20IPO%20made%20history%20with%20over%20Rs%2018%2C300%20crore%20share%20sale%20making%20it%20the%20largest%20public%20issue%20in%20India's%20corporate%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20company's%20stock%20made%20a%20weak%20debut%20in%20the%20market%20on%20November%2018%20and%20hit%20a%20lower%20circuit%20after%20recording%20about%2020%20per%20cent%20decline%20during%20trading%20hours.%20It%20finally%20closed%20at%20Rs%201%2C560%2C%20down%20by%20about%2027%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20firm's%20big%20backer%20SoftBank%20recently%20pared%20its%20stake%2C%20while%20other%20key%20investors%20Alibaba%20and%20Buffett's%20Berkshire%20Hathway%20sold%20their%20holdings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERevenue%20Sources%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm%20has%20two%20major%20sources%20of%20revenue%20-%20its%20merchant%20payment%20business%20and%20loan%20business.%20Merchant%20payments%20constitutes%20roughly%2060%25%20of%20total%20income%20and%20loans%20account%20for%20about%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fintech%20company%20charges%20merchants%20a%20platform%20fee%20to%20use%20Paytm's%20payment%20gateway%2C%20among%20other%20subscription-based%20services%20and%20products%20such%20as%20a%20soundbox%20and%20card%20swipe%20machine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20provides%20loans%20under%20partnerships%20with%20some%20banks%20and%20non-bank%20financial%20companies%2C%20taking%20a%20cut%20of%20the%20interest.%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20was%20one%20of%20these%20entities%20through%20which%20it%20provided%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERBI%20Crackdown%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20last%20week%20ordered%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20to%20wind%20down%20most%20of%20its%20businesses%2C%20including%20deposits%2C%20credit%20products%20and%20its%20popular%20wallet%20by%20February%2029%20for%20%26quot%3Bpersistent%20non-compliances%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsupervisory%20concerns%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20accounts%20created%20on%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20without%20proper%20identification%20were%20one%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20behind%20the%20RBI%20imposing%20stringent%20curbs%20on%20the%20company%2C%20reports%20quoted%20sources%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20is%20concerned%20that%20some%20of%20the%20accounts%20could%20have%20been%20used%20for%20money%20laundering%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20assuring%20users%2C%20Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%20has%20described%20the%20RBI's%20action%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bspeed%20bump%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707204000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-11%2Fcac3fqc8_vijay-shekhar-sharma-paytm-reuters-650_625x300_18_November_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpaytm-vijay-shekhar-sharma-rbi-paytm-wallet-paytms-vijay-shekhar-sharma-a-rags-to-riches-star-of-start-up-ecosystem-5003661%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20recognised%20faces%20of%20India's%20fintech%20industry%2C%20is%20facing%20a%20big%20crisis%20in%20a%20race%20to%20save%20his%20revolutionary%20digital%20payments%20firm%20-%20Paytm.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpaytm-vijay-shekhar-sharma-rbi-paytm-wallet-paytms-vijay-shekhar-sharma-a-rags-to-riches-star-of-start-up-ecosystem-5003661%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndt