0something%20wrong%20in%20the%20films%2C%20we%20also%20show%20that%20the%20result%20of%20it%20is%20something%20positive.%20Which%20is%20wrong.%20And%20we%20often%20make%20the%20women%20an%20'item'%20in%20films.%20Even%20the%20songs%20are%20like%20'%3Cem%3Etu%20cheez%20badi%20hai%20mast%20mast%3C%2Fem%3E'.%20And%20even%20I%20am%20involved%20in%20this%20and%20I%20have%20done%20such%20films.%20'%3Cem%3Ekhambe%20jaisi%20khadi%20hai%2C%20ladki%20hai%20ya%20chadi%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E.'%20We%20are%20calling%20women%20'%3Cem%3Ekhamba%3C%2Fem%3E'%20but%20not%20humans.%20I%20am%20very%20ashamed%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20post%20on%20X%20called%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga's%20attention%20to%20Aamir%20Khan's%20apology%20for%20participating%20in%20Bollywood's%20Nineties-era%20irresponsibility%20and%20asked%20if%20Mr%20Vanga%20would%20do%20the%20same%20for%20objectifying%20women%20in%20his%20own%20films%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELook%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fimvangasandeep%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40imvangasandeep%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FAamirKhan%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23AamirKhan%3C%2Fa%3E%20apologized%20in%20front%20of%20everyone%20for%20using%20%26quot%3Bkhambe%20jaisi%20khadi%26quot%3Bsong%20in%20Dil...will%20you%20ever%20do%20the%20same%20for%20showing%20women%20as%20objects%20in%20your%20movies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F22ypuOCTgb%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F22ypuOCTgb%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FbBBp7FjPJu%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FbBBp7FjPJu%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20RAJ%20(%40AamirsDevotee)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAamirsDevotee%2Fstatus%2F1753710303827959841%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKIRAN%20RA