%20figure%20as%20prominent%20as%20King%20Charles.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707194280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-10%2F9a6oea9o_prince-charles-william-harry-instagram_625x300_23_October_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-royal-commentator-told-ndtv-after-king-charles-iiis-cancer-diagnosis-5003045%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UK's%20King%20Charles%20III%20is%20undergoing%20treatment%20for%20cancer%2C%20triggering%20an%20outpouring%20of%20support%20from%20well-wishers%20worldwide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-royal-commentator-told-ndtv-after-king-charles-iiis-cancer-diagnosis-5003045%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-royal-commentator-told-ndtv-after-king-charles-iiis-cancer-diagnosis-5003045%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-royal-commentator-told-ndtv-after-king-charles-iiis-cancer-diagnosis-5003045%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Case%20Against%20Hockey%20Player%20Varun%20Kumar%20For%20Raping%20Minor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHockey%20player%20Varun%20Kumar%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20rape%20by%20a%20woman%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20-%20now%2022%20-%20alleged%20that%20Varun%20Kumar%20raped%20her%20several%20times%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20promising%20her%20of%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%2017%20when%20she%20met%20Varun%20Kumar%20through%20Instagram%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20alleged%20that%20Varun%20Kumar%20would%20have%20sex%20with%20her%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20Bengaluru's%20SAI%20stadium%20for%20hockey%20matches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20First%20information%20report%20or%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20th