%20robot%20to%20make%20it%20more%20accessible%20to%20the%20farmers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20an%20incident%20at%20Krishi%20Mela%20in%20Kota%2C%20Aryan%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20innovators%20around%20me%20and%20I%20was%20very%20nervous.%20But%20the%20robot%20garnered%20so%20much%20attention%20that%20hundreds%20of%20people%2C%20mostly%20farmers%2C%20visited%20my%20stall%20and%20showed%20interest%20in%20my%20work.%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20who%20is%20an%20MLA%20visited%20my%20stall%20and%20congratulated%20me%20on%20my%20innovation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20feels%20surreal%20but%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20I%20could%20bring%20such%20an%20innovation%20for%20the%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%3A%20Aryan%20Singh)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706885858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-4-1706885000.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D340703%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aryan%20Singh%20from%20Kota%2C%20an%2018-year-old%20recipient%20of%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Rashtriya%20Bal%20Puraskar%2C%20developed%20AgRobot%20%E2%80%94%20an%20AI-powered%20rover%20to%20assist%20farmers%20in%20reducing%20the%20burden%20of%20farm%20labour.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340703%2Fkota-student-aryan-singh-invented-ai-powered-agrobot-runs-on-solar-energy%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tesla%20Recalling%20Nearly%202.2%20Million%20Vehicles%20To%20Fix%20Warning%20Lights%20That%20Are%20Too%20Small%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22U.S.%20safety%20regulators%20say%20the%20recall%20will%20be%20done%20with%20an%20online%20software%20update.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706875529000%2C%22