hose%20days%2C%20children%20were%20not%20taught%20about%20good%20touch%20and%20bad%20touch%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20then%20when%20she%20was%2013%2C%20Mansi%20says%20she%20was%20molested%20by%20a%20house%20help.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20It%20was%20not%20a%20stranger%20exactly%2C%20and%20I%20did%20not%20know%20who%20to%20turn%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20did%20turn%20to%20my%20mother%20for%20help%2C%20I%20was%20too%20scared%20to%20open%20up%20about%20it%20to%20anyone%20else%2C%20so%20I%20pushed%20myself%20into%20a%20shell.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20abuse%20continued%20and%20Mansi%20kept%20suffering%20in%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSchool%20was%20no%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20this%20trauma%20and%20abuse%20was%20affecting%20my%20growth.%20I%20was%20not%20good%20at%20academics%20and%20I%20did%20not%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20friends.%20All%20I%20had%20in%20school%20was%20bullies%20and%20abuse.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20the%20constant%20abuse%20led%20her%20to%20believe%20that%20it%20was%20something%20she%20deserved.%20%E2%80%9CAbuse%20became%20my%20normal%20and%20comfort%20zone.%20These%20experiences%20primed%20me%20for%20dissociation.%20Even%20now%2C%20I%20can%20easily%20slip%20into%20a%20mental%20space%20where%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20fully%20present%2C%20where%20my%20body%20and%20mind%20disconnect.%20This%20dissociation%20is%20one%20of%20the%20lasting%20effects%20of%20abuse.%20Surprisingly%2C%20it%20led%20me%20towards%20more%20such%20instances%20in%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20myself%20and%20breaking%20the%20cycle%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20in%20school%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20a%20teacher%20when%20I%20was%2015.%20It%20took%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20strength%20to%20open%20up%2C%20but%20she%20did%20not%20believe%20me.%2