C%20and%20dislikes%20within%20the%20existing%20school.%20Similarly%2C%20I%20engaged%20in%20discussions%20with%20teachers%20to%20explore%20ways%20to%20enhance%20the%20learning%20environment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Anand%20also%20started%20to%20visit%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338824%2Fmuskaan-dreams-abhishek-dubey-introduces-technology-in-rural-school-education-digital-literacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20schools%20for%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20visual%20impairment%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Victoria%20Memorial%20School%20for%20the%20Blind%20in%20Mumbai%20left%20a%20lasting%20impression%20on%20me%20because%20of%20its%20remarkable%20beauty%2C%20despite%20being%20an%20adaptively%20reused%20building.%20However%2C%20I%20found%20very%20few%20good%20examples%20of%20schools%20specifically%20designed%20for%20users%20with%20disabilities.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20I%20later%20volunteered%20at%20the%20Perkins%20School%20for%20the%20Blind%20in%20Massachusetts%2C%20one%20of%20the%20oldest%20schools%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20Established%20in%201829%2C%20it%20boasts%20a%20rich%20history%20with%20stalwarts%20like%20Helen%20Keller%2C%20Laura%20Bridgman%2C%20and%20Anne%20Sullivan%20who%20all%20studied%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20found%20wonderful%20mentors%20in%20the%20US%20and%20was%20able%20to%20find%20the%20right%20direction%20for%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20went%20out%20looking%20for%20inspiration%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20it%20was%20not%20one%20place%20that%20could%20help%20me%20but%20a%20lot.%20Visiting%20various%20schools%20was%20a%20great%20learning%20arc%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUsing%20five%20senses%20to%20navigate%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20is%20des