0types%20of%20wall%20plasters%20and%20textures%20for%20students%20to%20identify%20spaces.%20Additionally%2C%20for%20ease%20of%20navigation%2C%20we%20utilised%20different%20textures%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20incorporating%20rough%20and%20smooth%20Kota%20stone%2C%20which%20marks%20the%20entry%20points%20of%20the%20classrooms%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20area%20classroom%2C%20corridor%2C%20and%20courtyard%20in%20the%20school%20is%20marked%20and%20written%20in%20Braille.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHearing%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20another%20navigation%20technique%20that%20utilises%20hearing%2C%20Anand%20varies%20the%20volumes%20and%20heights%20of%20the%20buildings%2C%20creating%20different%20echoes%20and%20sounds%20to%20assist%20students%20in%20identifying%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20school%20features%20a%20wide%20and%20tall%20volume%2C%20while%20the%20opposite%20side%20has%20a%20shorter%20volume%20and%20is%20narrower.%20This%20contrast%20in%20width%20and%20height%20produces%20a%20distinct%20echo%20compared%20to%20the%20entrance.%20Students%2C%20as%20part%20of%20their%20training%2C%20walk%2C%20talk%2C%20and%20even%20clap%20to%20practise%20using%20different%20techniques%20for%20identifying%20spaces%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESight%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20navigation%20easy%20for%20students%20who%20can%20perceive%20colour%20in%20light%2C%20he%20used%20different%20colours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGiven%20that%20many%20low%20vision%20students%20are%20studying%20in%20the%20school%2C%20another%20aspect%20we%20had%20to%20consider%20was%20using%20contrasting%20colours%20and%20lighting%20to%20help%20students%20identify%20objects%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F320628%2Fheta-pandit-writes-stories-from-goan-homes-book-on-culture-family-food%2