%20card%20services%2C%20payment%20of%20household%20bills%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20was%20a%20two-year%20course%2C%20he%20only%20studied%20there%20for%20a%20year%20because%20of%20the%20national%20lockdown%20imposed%20following%20COVID-19.%20It%20was%20at%20this%20institute%20where%20he%20started%20learning%20English.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20weren%E2%80%99t%20allowed%20regular%20access%20to%20our%20mobile%20phones.%20Every%20Saturday%2C%20they%20would%20allow%20us%20to%20use%20our%20phones%20for%20three%20hours.%20Back%20then%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20a%20smartphone.%20I%20had%20a%20Jio%20phone%20with%20basic%20features.%20During%20one%20such%20session%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20video%20%5Bon%20YouTube%5D%20where%20I%20found%20someone%20teaching%20how%20to%20connect%20words%20and%20shorten%20them%20in%20spoken%20English%20conversation.%20That%20captivated%20me%20and%20I%20was%20interested%20to%20learn%20that%20kind%20of%20English%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Dhiraj%20left%20Kerala%2C%20he%20began%20learning%20the%20%5BAmerican%5D%20accent%20that%20he%20currently%20employs%20in%20his%20reels%20by%20watching%20a%20plethora%20of%20videos%20online.%20Also%2C%20by%20the%20time%20he%20came%20back%20home%20to%20his%20village%2C%20he%20had%20a%20basic%20Panasonic%20P91%20smartphone%20with%20a%204G%20internet%20connection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20motivation%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20speak%20English%20in%20that%20manner%20came%20from%20a%20desire%20to%20communicate%20faster.%20As%20he%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20used%20to%20speak%20English%20very%20slowly.%20Learning%20how%20to%20speak%20in%20an%20%5BWestern%5D%20accent%20was%20more%20about%20learning%20to%20speak%20the%20language%20faster.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20at%20the%20time%2C%20I%20had%20an%20interest%20in%20singing%20English%20songs%20like%20those%20in%20the%20West%20do.%20If%20I%20wanted%20to%20sing%20in%20their%20accent%2C%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20to%20speak%20in%20their%20accent%20too.%20At%20the%20institute%20in%20Kerala%2C%20I%20developed%20a%20strong%20interest%20in%20learning%20the%20English%20language%2C%20and%20the%20desire%20to%20speak%20it%20faster%20and%20in%20a%20Western%20accent.%20But%20since%20our%20access%20to%20mobile%20phones%20was%20limited%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20learn%20much.%20When%20I%20came%20back%20home%20during%20the%20lockdown%20with%20all%20the%20free%20time%20in%20the%20world%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20started%20learning%20and%20practising%20the%20accent%20you%20hear%20in%20my%20reels%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20during%20the%20lockdown%2C%20Dhiraj%20learnt%20how%20to%20edit%20photos%20and%20videos%20not%20out%20of%20a%20desire%20to%20make%20reels%20but%20just%20for%20fun.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%20learning%20how%20to%20edit%20photos%20and%20videos%20and%20watch%20the%20work%20of%20other%20content%20makers%20online%2C%20my%20village%20had%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274123%2Fiit-bombay-student-brings-cellular-connectivity-remote-himachal-pradesh-village%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E4G%20connectivity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20a%20smartphone%2C%20I%20could%20watch%20videos%20and%20pick%20up%20these%20skills%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC2KonTyh2-K%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDhiraj-Takri-Instagram-1706621044.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dhiraj%20Takri%20went%20viral%20on%20Instagram%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%