20support%20from%20his%20mother%2C%20who%20is%20the%20co-founder%20of%20ALVE%20Green%20Solutions%2C%20he%20worked%20diligently%20for%20over%20eight%20months.%20It%20took%20more%20than%2020%20prototypes%20before%20achieving%20the%20ideal%20result%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20professors%20saw%20this%2C%20they%20were%20amazed.%20They%20said%20that%20this%20needs%20to%20be%20given%20to%20a%20bigger%20audience%20and%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%20They%20helped%20me%20perfect%20it%20with%20the%20help%20of%20machines%20in%20the%20college%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rajiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20smart%2C%20zero-plastic%20air%20freshener%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22alve%20air%20fresheners%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339845%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThese%20air%20fresheners%20are%20eco-friendly%2C%20smart%20and%20made%20of%20floral%20waste%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20freshener%20is%20available%20in%20three%20variants%20for%20homes%2C%20offices%2C%20and%20cars%2C%20offering%20a%20choice%20of%2015%20fragrances.%20Each%20unit%20is%20equipped%20with%20smart%20sensors%20that%20automatically%20activate%20and%20deactivate%20based%20on%20the%20detection%20of%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20presence.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20is%20compatible%20with%20Google%20Assistant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20freshener%20features%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Ftopics%2Fsustainability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiodegradable%20body%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20be%20composted%20after%20use%2C%20and%20its%20refills%20are%20organic%20%E2%80%94%20crafted%20from%20temple%20flower%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20nature%E2%80%99s%20intelligence%20in%20retaining%20the%20fragrances.%20Chemical%20fresheners%20use%20LPG%20to%20retain%20the%20fragrance.%20We%20use%20natural%20ingredients%20for%20that%20with%20no%20chemicals.%20We%20do%20not%20use%20any%20heat%2C%20water%20vapour%20or%20chemicals%20to%20diffuse%20our%20fragrances.%20We%20use%20our%20own%20Air%20Diffusion%20Technology%20with%20sensors%20to%20diffuse%20aroma%20evenly%20in%20the%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajiv%20has%20partnered%20with%20more%20than%2030%20temples%20in%20Jamshedpur%20to%20obtain%20floral%20waste.%20Every%20day%2C%20he%20collects%20a%20minimum%20of%203%20kg%20of%20floral%20waste%20from%20each%20temple.%20To%20date%2C%20he%20has%20recycled%201%2C500%20kg%20of%20temple%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20noteworthy%20aspect%20is%20that%20this%20freshener%20is%20safe%20for%20animals%20also.%20Working%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20Animal%20Welfare%20Society%20since%202018%2C%20Rajiv%20was%20shocked%20by%20the%20effects%20of%20human%20behaviour%20on%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3